result.name: Green Waffle Diner

reviews.text: Green Waffle dinner is conveniently placed on the ground floor of Yoho Mall 1 and serviced by friendly staff. We arrived at 3:30pm and were seated immediately. I used the easy QR code to open the menu and order with my phone. Our waffles arrived soon after, exactly to order. Food was fresh and yummy, not the best waffle I’ve ever had, but a delicious treat nonetheless.

If you can’t go eat this place at causeway bay or central, then drive here to eat. In my experience (at lunch), service is nice and spacious. They can let you order by phone when they distribute the QR code to you!

Last week I have tried this new branch with friend. Overall, it’s very delicious!

I have ordered avocado toast with scrambled egg. The egg is very creamy; perfectly cooked. Avocado is soft and creamy and the bread / sourdough is slightly toasted; you can get the crunchiness from the bread and the creamy texture from the egg and avocado, a very good combination.

And then my friend has chosen set dinner, a 3-course dinner - Salad/Soup + Main + Dessert w/ drinks.

We finally chose Buffalo Chicken with roasted corn and 🍠 yam fries. We are surprised that they have offered a generous portion of the main course. Three huge chicken legs, 2 🌽 and a bunch of yam. All of them are very tasty, chicken is moist and well seasoned. Corn is not dried and the yam slightly sweet and crispy in the inside. Last but not least, waffle is their set dinner dessert, make to order, fluffy, served with icecream (we finally chose vanilla) and seasonal fruit, refreshing, a great ending of our dinner night! Highly recommended!
Their banana pancake tea set is awesome!
a bit pricy with standard food, seat are very close to each other

result.adr_address: 9 Long Yat Rd, Yuen Long, Hong Kong
result.formatted_address: 9 Long Yat Rd, Yuen Long, Hong Kong
result.name: YOHO MALL I

reviews.text: A clean, well organised mall with more stores than you can imagine. Well maintained and hygienic restrooms as frequently spaced and the proximity to the MTR is a big plus!

Huge variety! It's great for shopping and dining 👍 they also have a cinema, for entertainment, showing a variety of Western and Asian movies. Pop-up stalls and exhibitions are constantly visiting the mall giving shoppers something interesting to do while walking from shop to shop, or just to celebrate the current events (popular movies, holidays, brands etc.)

Nothing special different from other plaza
It’s crowded. Many mainland people surrounded. 
Although it’s so many restaurant, you need to queue for the restaurant was extremely long.
And the price is not reasonable.
Very disappointed. 
Not recommend.
a grand n morden mall with variaties of dinning places, great to visit...

Many restaurants & cafe, you can find any kind of food & style, this should be the biggest shopping mall at Yuen Long area at moment, very convenient and easy to access, just a min. walk linked with West Rail Yuen Long station.

result.name: Green Waffle Diner

I used the easy QR code to open the menu and order with my phone. Our waffles arrived soon after, exactly to order. Food was fresh and yummy, not the best waffle I’ve ever had, but a delicious treat nonetheless.

好耐無係yoho行過，估唔到又開左幾多新餐廳，今次就入黎其中一間試下先！餐廳環境都幾靚，好有親近大自然既感覺，而且餐廳環境都幾闊落。

同一般西餐廳分別唔大，不過最特別既係佢有勁多all day breakfast，仲有一頁薯粒鑊仔都係幾特別，仲有一個smoothies bowl又係勁想試，不過今次黎食夜晚，下次brunch個啲位黎食先試下

朋友想食扒，而我又無乜興趣，所以就嗌左個沙律試下啦

朋友既starter轉左做水牛城雞翼(小辣)，食過咁多唔同既水牛城雞翼黎講依個都算出色，多汁得黎個雞翼仲係脆既，辣得黎又唔會好供鼻

燒烤豬串骨伴薯蓉及烤栗米($198)

水煮蛋火腿雜菜沙律配黑醋沙律汁($98) 估唔到咁大碟

朋友個餐最後仲包左個甜品 - 窩夫伴雪榚及新鮮生果，窩夫係新鮮整好既，上黎既時候仲係暖暖地，配埋雪榚、糖漿一齊食真係無得頂

今晚朋友想食西餐,揀咗yoho mall🍽，交通夠哂方便，餐廳簡潔清新，在四週有許多綠色植物陪襯下進餐，份外舒適🌿☘🍀😌     
10安士安格斯肉眼扒配薯菜$238.00  
頭盤凱撒沙律~ 新鮮、爽脆👍 肉眼扒~ 外邊煎得微微焦香，有🐮味、有肉汁， 配埋酸忌廉焗薯，冇得輸😋
五殼蟹蕃茄乾意大利飯$142.00香香脆脆，🍚 充滿茄味🍅🍅，軟硬適中， 啱曬我哋條👅 
奇異果果汁$48.00
~新鮮果汁☺
最後來個鮮果 窩夫配雲呢拿雪糕作美好嘅完結😋☺
👩‍⚖ 食物幾高質素，服務有禮， 採取電子系統點餐👍 餐廳走塑用紙飲筒👍 食西餐有多一個選擇😙

點了個dinner set， 烤豬寸骨 配一份窩夫雪糕， 另外再點咗個 勁量早餐！
豬寸骨都算烤得幾惹味， 以一間專食鍋嘅專門店嚟講算係幾有水準👍
之後上長嘅主角就係窩夫配雪糕， 只是賣相已夠滿足我們😍
味道都當然非常之好啦， 本身用嘅醬料同窩夫配合得好好， 食完之後真係發覺 唔夠喉😆
之後嘅勁量早餐真係非常之勁量， 雖然味道真係好好， 但對於兩位女生來說，分量始終太大😅

難得入元朗行街，見到呢一間餐廳裝修得幾靚幾清新，一於試下！

佢嘅餐牌封面推介鑊仔系列，一於試下！我地揀左Mac and cheese🧀 

一上菜就流曬口水，佢個煎pan勁熱，d芝士醬仲喺上邊跳緊舞，仲多到浸滿所有通粉！😆小心個pan，真係好熱😂一食落口，佢果隻鹹香濃郁充滿成個口，味蕾上嘅享受難以用言語形容🥰🥰🥰唔係間間嘅芝士都好味，但係呢一間真係一流😍

食完呢個主菜都真係幾飽，我地跟住點左個甜品🍮藍莓香蕉士多啤梨窩夫，好多新鮮嘅水果，而且士多啤梨都係甜嘅😝最令人驚喜嘅係佢嘅窩夫，果然係主打！😍外脆內軟，奶味和蛋味平衡得啱啱好，就咁食都已經覺得非常好食😆😆😆🥰😍加埋綠茶雪糕或者忌廉去食又係另一種層次同口感！不過講真，就咁單食都已經令人好滿意！😆😆

就算我第二度食完主菜，都會揀嚟呢度食甜品，超高質！🤩
